<!--
  Launcher icon foreground: the wordmark "N" with a bite taken out of it.

  The N is the real Bagel Fat One glyph, extracted from the shipped font file and
  converted to a path, so the icon and the in-app wordmark are the same letterform
  rather than a lookalike.

  Everything sits inside the 66dp safe zone of the 108dp viewport — adaptive icons
  are cropped to roughly 72dp and then masked, so art outside that gets eaten.
-->
